OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1783691326
OL,3,CGreek man found guilty of 2009 murder
OL,4,Cof British expat in Crete
OL,6,FITV News Reporter Natalie Higgins
OL,7,Flooks back on Jean Hanlon's family's
OL,8,Flong fight for justice
OL,10,FA man in his 50s has been sentenced to
OL,11,Ften years in prison for murdering a
OL,12,FScottish woman on a Greek island 17
OL,13,Fyears ago.
OL,15,FThe body of 53-year-old Jean Hanlon,
OL,16,Ffrom Dumfries, was recovered from the
OL,17,Fwater at Heraklion harbour in Crete in
OL,18,FMarch 2009.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
